llying around a family that suffered a tragic loss in a house fire almost two weeks ago.</p>',1348747336,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Thu, 27 Sep 2012 06:10:37 EDT',NULL,'CBC | New Brunswick News',NULL,'<img width=\"460\" height=\"259\" src=\"http://www.cbc.ca/gfx/images/news/topstories/2012/09/27/hi-nb-tracadie-fire-852-6col.jpg\"><br/><p>The northeastern community of Tracadie-Sheila is rallying around a family that suffered a tragic loss in a house fire almost two weeks ago.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(103,0,0,'Grand Manan ferry fees continue despite plebiscite vote','text/html','http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/story/2012/09/26/nb-grand-manan-ferry-fares.html?cmp=rss','Province',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,5,'<img width=\"460\" height=\"259\" src=\"http://www.cbc.ca/gfx/images/news/topstories/2012/07/13/hi-nb-grand-manan-ferry-0712-852-6col.jpg\"><br/><p>Grand Manan residents are still paying to use the island&apos;s ferry four months after they voted in a plebiscite to ask the Alward government to live up to its 2010 election promise to scrap them.</p>',1348747336,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Thu, 27 Sep 2012 06:13:32 EDT',NULL,'CBC | New Brunswick News',NULL,'<img width=\"460\" height=\"259\" src=\"http://www.cbc.ca/gfx/images/news/topstories/2012/07/13/hi-nb-grand-manan-ferry-0712-852-6col.jpg\"><br/><p>Grand Manan residents are still paying to use the island&apos;s ferry four months after they voted in a plebiscite to ask the Alward government to live up to its 2010 election promise to scrap them.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(104,0,0,'Saint John skateboarders face mandatory helmet bylaw','text/html','http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/story/2012/09/27/nb-skateboard-helmet-bylaw-742.html?cmp=rss','Province',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,5,'<img width=\"460\" height=\"259\" src=\"http://www.cbc.ca/gfx/images/news/topstories/2012/09/17/hi-longboard-852-6col.jpg\"><br/><p>Saint John is trying to impose new rules that would force skateboarders to wear a helmet on city streets, but city politicians may have a difficult time enforcing the new amendments.</p>',1348747336,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Thu, 27 Sep 2012 07:11:40 EDT',NULL,'CBC | New Brunswick News',NULL,'<img width=\"460\" height=\"259\" src=\"http://www.cbc.ca/gfx/images/news/topstories/2012/09/17/hi-longboard-852-6col.jpg\"><br/><p>Saint John is trying to impose new rules that would force skateboarders to wear a helmet on city streets, but city politicians may have a difficult time enforcing the new amendments.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(105,0,0,'Curtis Bonnell pulled knife during arrest for Hilary&apos;s death','text/html','http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/story/2012/09/26/nb-curtis-bonnell-hilary-arrest-knife.html?cmp=rss','Province',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,5,'<img width=\"460\" height=\"259\" src=\"http://www.cbc.ca/gfx/images/news/topstories/2012/09/17/nb-hi-curtisbonnell-6col.jpg\"><br/><p>Curtis Bonnell pulled a knife and barricaded himself inside his house when police went to arrest him in connection with the death of Hilary Bonnell in 2009, a jury heard on Wednesday.</p>',1348747336,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Wed, 26 Sep 2012 17:39:36 EDT',NULL,'CBC | New Brunswick News',NULL,'<img width=\"460\" height=\"259\" src=\"http://www.cbc.ca/gfx/images/news/topstories/2012/09/17/nb-hi-curtisbonnell-6col.jpg\"><br/><p>Curtis Bonnell pulled a knife and barricaded himself inside his house when police went to arrest him in connection with the death of Hilary Bonnell in 2009, a jury heard on Wednesday.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(106,0,0,'$1M lotto prize remains unclaimed','text/html','http://www.cbc.ca/news/canad