 purchasing of an automobile over the phone using stolen credit card information. The caller uses a fictitious name, provides the car dealership with a credit card number and tells the dealer that a towing company will look after shipping arrangements. Car dealers and towing companies only discover after the transaction has been concluded and the car has been shipped that the credit card information was stolen  ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(213,0,0,'Single vehicle collision claims life of 25-year-old man,  Rang-Saint-Georges, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/12-09-24-154555-eng.htm','City',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,'A 25-year-old Maltempec, N.B. man has died following a single vehicle collision on September 23, 2012.',1348775057,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Tue, 25 Sep 2012 11:47:00 -0330',NULL,'Royal Canadian Mounted Police in New Brunswick',NULL,'A 25-year-old Maltempec, N.B. man has died following a single vehicle collision on September 23, 2012.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(214,0,0,'Woman arrested for attempted armed robbery, Oromocto, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/12-10-22-144637-eng.htm','City',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,'District 2 RCMP in Oromocto has arrested a 30-year-old woman in connection with an armed robbery that took place at an Oromocto restaurant on September 18, 2012.',1348775057,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Mon, 24 Sep 2012 11:02:40 -0330',NULL,'Royal Canadian Mounted Police in New Brunswick',NULL,'District 2 RCMP in Oromocto has arrested a 30-year-old woman in connection with an armed robbery that took place at an Oromocto restaurant on September 18, 2012.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(215,0,0,'Man charged in connection with break and enters, Grande Digue, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/12-09-24-122405-eng.htm','City',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,'District 4 RCMP in Shediac have arrested and charged a man in connection with numerous break and enters in the Grande Digue and Caissie Cape areas.',1348775058,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Mon, 24 Sep 2012 14:30:47 -0330',NULL,'Royal Canadian Mounted Police in New Brunswick',NULL,'District 4 RCMP in Shediac have arrested and charged a man in connection with numerous break and enters in the Grande Digue and Caissie Cape areas.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(216,0,0,'Drug Seizure, St Stephen, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/12-09-24-093440-eng.htm','City',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,'Two St. Stephen, N.B. men have been arrested after District 1 RCMP searched a home and seized a quantity of drugs.',1348775058,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Mon, 24 Sep 2012 12:12:16 -0330',NULL,'Royal Canadian Mounted Police in New Brunswick',NULL,'Two St. Stephen, N.B. men have been arrested after District 1 RCMP searched a home and seized a quantity of drugs.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(217,0,0,'Crime Stoppers Crime of the Week - Break, Enter and Theft, Fredericton, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/12-09-21-125604-eng.htm','City',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,'Crime Stoppers and the Fredericton Police Force are looking for the person responsible for several break, enter and thefts in Fredericton, New Brunswick. On Saturday, January 7, 2012, between 2:30 a.m. and 6:00 a.m., break-ins occurred at apartments located at 237 and 245 York Street, and 380 Charlotte Street in Fredericton.\n',1348775058,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Mon, 24 Sep 2012 10:23:01 -0330',NULL,'Royal Canadian Mounted Police in New Brunswick',NULL,'Crime Stoppers and the Fredericton Police Force are looking for the person responsible for several break, enter and thefts in Fredericton, New Brunswick. On Saturday, January 7, 2012, between 2:30 a.m. and 6:00 a.m., break-ins occurred at apartments located at 237 and 245 York Street, and 380 Charlotte Street in Fredericton.\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(218,0,0,'Body of missing woman discovered in Moncton, Moncton, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/12-09-23-195144-eng.htm','City',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,'The body of 29-year-old Alanna Greene of Moncton, who was reported missing on September17, 2012 has been discovered in Mapleton Park in Moncton. \n',1348775058,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Sun, 23 Sep 2012 19:50:45 -0330',NULL,'Royal Canadian Mounted Police in New Brunswick',NULL,'The body of 29-year-old Alanna Greene of Moncton, who was reported missing on September17, 2012 has been discovered in Mapleton Park in Moncton. \n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Posted','25','News','Police',NULL),(219,0,0,'Man in custody after home invasion and sexual assault, Shediac, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/12-09-22-105505-eng.htm','City',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,'District 4 RCMP members have arrested a 21 year old Shediac in relation to a home invasion and a sexual assault. ',1348775058,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Sat, 22 Sep 2012 10:53:35 -0330',NULL,'Royal Canadian Mounted Police in New Brunswick',NULL,'District 4 RCMP members have arrested a 21 year old Shediac in relation to a home invasion and a sexual assault. ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(220,0,0,'Body of missing man recovered from Saint John River, Aroostook, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/12-09-22-104729-eng.htm','City',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,NULL,1348775058,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Sat, 22 Sep 2012 10:47:08 -0330',NULL,'Royal Canadian Mounted Police in New Brunswick',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(221,0,0,'Man arrested in connection with child sexual abuse image investigation, Burton, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/12-09-21-144047-eng.htm','City',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,'On September 20, 2012, investigators with the RCMP&apos;s ICE Unit, the Saint John Police Force, the RCMP&apos;s Technological Crime Unit and District 2 RCMP searched a home in Burton and seized various items including computer equipment and data storage devices containing images of children being sexually abused. A 43-year-old man was arrested. He was later released on strict conditions to not be in contact with children under 16 years of age and not to have access to a computer.  ',1348775058,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fri, 21 Sep 2012 14:41:25 -0330',NULL,'Royal Canadian Mounted Police in New Brunswick',NULL,'On September 20, 2012, investigators with the RCMP&apos;s ICE Unit, the Saint John Police Force, the RCMP&apos;s Technological Crime Unit and District 2 RCMP searched a home in Burton and seized various items including computer equipment and data storage devices containing images of children being sexually abused. A 43-year-old man was arrested. He was later released on strict conditions to not be in contact with children under 16 years of age and not to have access to a computer.  ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Fresh',NULL,'News','News',NULL),(222,0,0,'Teenager pleads guilty to stealing a truck, Sussex, N.B.','text/html','http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvell